                    BARD'S TALE ITEMS LIST
                    ----------------------

(1)   DRAGON FIGURINE -- CREATES A DRAGON FOR YOUR SPECIAL SLOT.
(2)   MAGE FIGURINE   -- CREATES A MAGE FOR YOUR SPECIAL SLOT.
(3)   TROLL RING      -- DOES THE SAME AS KIEL'S MAGIC COMPASS.
(4)   TROLL STAFF     -- UNKOWN.
(5)   ONYX KEY        -- USED TO OPEN EITHER THE GATE TO MANGAR'S                                         TOWER
                         OR KYLEAREAN'S TOWER.
(6)   CRYSTAL SWORD   -- USED TO KILL CRYSTAL GOLEM.
(7)   STONEBLADE      -- SWORD THAT TURNS MONSTERS TO STONE WHEN ,
                         STRUCK WITH IT.
(8)   TRAVELHELM      -- DOES THE SAME AS APPORT ARCANE (TELEPORT 
                         SPELL).
(9)   DEATH DAGGER    -- UNKNOWN.
(10)  MONGO FIGURINE  -- SUMMONS A POWERFUL MONSTER TO YOUR SPECIAL                                       SLOT.
(11)  LICH FIGURINE   -- SUMMONS A LICH TO YOUR SPECIAL SLOT.
(12)  EYE             -- USED TO MAKE STATUE OF MAD GOD COME ALIVE.
(13)  MASTER KEY      -- EITHER USED TO OPEN GATES TO MANGAR'S TOWER OR
                         KYLEAREAN'S TOWER.
(14)  WIZ WAND        -- UNKNOWN.
(15)  SILVR CIRCLE    -- ONE OF THE GEOMETRIC FIGURES TO GET PAST A
                         POINT IN MANGAR'S TOWER.
(16)  SILVR TRIANGLE  -- ONE OF THE ITEMS USED TO GET PAST A POINT IN
                         MANGAR'S TOWER.
