                             T O M   M I C H A U D


                       MAGICAL ITEMS AND WEAPONS

      This chart will tell you about most of the items you will find in 
     the realm.  The first number tells if it is magical or non-magical.
     The second letter will tell you if thereis any other possible use
     for the item.

                       0.non-magical          1. magical                                                  
 
                             1. lowers a.c. count
                             2. cast spells
                             3. breath fire/frost
                             4. create figurine

                               BEGINNER TIPS
  
          When possible equip your magic users with mage staff.
         This allows them to regenerate spell points in a dungeon.

